data.text: Meenei God, hagalongo mai gi dagu gahigahi.
I lodo hua dogu manawa gee mo dogu mogowaa i dogu guongo,
idimaa Goe go dogu abaaba, dogu Dangada daa maaloo
Heia au gii noho i lodo doo hale dabu i di waalooloo o dogu mouli,
Meenei God, Goe gu longono agu hagababa,
Haga waalooloo ina di mouli o di king. Heia a mee gi mouli hua beelaa!
Meenei God, heia a mee gi dagi hua beelaa i oo mua
Gei au ga dadaahili laa i nia madagoaa huogodoo e hagaamu Goe,
